snippet.title: Autechre - Amber (Album Review)
snippet.description:
The other Incunabula that seems to have eclipsed the debut for many people and even first introduced me to this duo.
Support me on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/TheWonkyAngle

More Autechre reviews: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL9VloxGOomL4ImOtIL2DKyMRIM1mFpIim
Listen: https://open.spotify.com/album/7EfhvG3RwdhzXrFlkDVxg4

Favorite Tracks: Montreal, Silverside, Slip, Further, Yulquen, Teartear
Least Favorite Track: Nil
Overall Rating: 7.7/10

All ratings based purely off of personal enjoyment at the time of this video's upload and either end in .0, .3, .5, or .7. Take nothing I say too seriously.
